object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct StateLine,
 case when stateline=1 then '010'  when stateline=2 then '021' when stateline=4 then '040'  when stateline=8 then '051' when stateline=9 then '090'   else null  end as ASL,
 ReinsNumber, Company, State, Year, month ,Premium,RowInsDt
FROM dbo.Reins_CAT_Premium
where month   in('January','Jan','April','Apr','July','Jul','October','Oct')
and  TO_CHAR(RowInsDt, 'YYYYMMDD') in(select max(TO_CHAR(RowInsDt, 'YYYYMMDD') ) FROM dbo.Reins_CAT_Premium)
